306A(d), or § 47-9-306B(b)".
SECTION 85. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 47-9-316(f), is amended by deleting
the subsection and substituting:
(f) Change in jurisdiction of chattel paper, controllable electronic record,
bank, issuer, nominated person, securities intermediary, or commodity
intermediary. A security interest in chattel paper, controllable accounts, controllable
electronic records, controllable payment intangibles, deposit accounts, letter-of-credit
rights, or investment property that is perfected under the law of the chattel paper's
